title: Miley Cyrus flashes skin in bizarre outfit
text:
Known for her bizarre fashion sense, singer Miley Cyrus again made heads turn when she stepped out here in a graphic shirt dress with sheer panels on the chest and hip parts, flashing her underb**b and panties.

She kept herself warm with a sky blue denim jacket and blue stockings paired with combat boots. She sported a multicolored dread locked hair extension and wore sunglasses although it was dark outside. She also carried a Unicorn Tears bag and held a beverage in one hand, reports aceshowbiz.com.

The 22-year-old is gearing up to host the season 41 premiere of "Saturday Night Live" airing this weekend. In a promo which also features regular cast member Taran Killam, she teases that she will be hosting "with or without clothes - we're not sure yet". In another sketch, Cyrus reveals what she will wear on the variety series.
